      "name": "VAD operating envelope — flow and speed bounds",
      "description": "Five nominal operating points spanning flow rates 3–8 L/min and rotational speeds 2400–3600 RPM. Inlet pressure 5–15 mmHg; outlet pressure 60–120 mmHg. All points lie within the validated operating envelope of the FDA generic pump geometry."
    }
  },
