      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver confirming second-order spatial convergence. Power-law hemolysis transport equation verified against analytical solution for simple Couette flow.",
